data.description: This two-story, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home in Lincoln Park is turnkey and ready for it's new homeowners! The home has new interior paint and the abundance of bright lighting and hardwood floors throughout create a warm and inviting atmosphere. With two living spaces and two dining areas, there's plenty of room for both relaxation and entertaining.The spacious kitchen is a standout feature, offering an island with a breakfast bar and a convenient walk-in pantry. This layout provides ample counter space and storage options for your culinary needs. All the bedrooms are situated upstairs, providing privacy and separation from the main living areas. The primary bedroom is particularly impressive, featuring a unique ensuite bathroom with separate vanities, allowing for individual space, as well as two walk-in closets, providing generous storage for your belongings. There are two additional bedrooms and an extra full bathroom to accommodate family members or guests. The large backyard adds to the appeal of the home, with a patio and mature trees that provide shade and a pleasant aesthetic. It's a perfect space for relaxation or hosting gatherings. The Lincoln Park community is located near a variety of shopping, restaurants, and entertainment that is convenience and accessible for daily life. Click the Virtual Tour link to view the 3D walkthrough.
